A page from the technical specification of deployed drones
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
AMPV


The Advanced Multi-Purpose Vehicle (AMPV) is often referred to as "Tank".
It is a heavily armored, all-terrain unit that is usually deployed to guard strategic positions.
This unit's detection radius is limited, but its robustness, speed and offensive strength compensate for it.


Armor type: Heavy

Weapon type: Double machine gun

Damage: 4

Chassis type: Tracks (Can cross plain and rough terrain. Cannot swim.)

Max Life: 30

Speed factor: 2


Weaknesses: 


The detection radius of the AMPV is limited, especially at night.
AMPV's armor protects it from all but heaviest weapons, such as machine guns and rocket launchers.


 

 



  